      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="select_submission_type" data-step-uuid="e4530f9a-fcfe-4fbc-bd38-a1737a3b68ff">
    <h2 id="select_submission_type" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Submission Type</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/394/336/original/5f5aab9b-b017-4c58-ba06-0ed15e84f3da.png" srcset="" alt="Select Submission Type" height="222" width="542">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_0F86C0B0-1E4B-0135-039C-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Submission Type</strong> drop-down menu [1], and select your preferred<strong> </strong>submission type [2]. </p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>The External Tool submission type does not support peer review assignments.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="select_online_entry_options" data-step-uuid="06660b8c-f28b-4e84-a290-5866920aebb1">
